                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .55in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.3in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: 42.55pt; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">10.3.</span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">The minimum amount required to withdrawal earnings is 100, depending on the currency to which your account is set. Transactions made on www.stxcapital.net will be represented on your billing statement as www.stxcapital.net phone:44-2035192136.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .55in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 15.0pt; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">&nbsp;</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .25in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; background: black;"><b><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">Bonuses. </span></b></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .55in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.3in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: 42.55pt; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.1.</span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">All bonuses and promotions offered by&nbsp;Staxcapital&nbsp;are subject to several conditions, including but not limited to minimum deposit amounts, minimum trading volume and any other requirements detailed within the specific offer.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .55in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.3in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: 42.55pt; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.2.</span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">In order to redeem a bonus, clients must meet&nbsp;Staxcapital's&nbsp;required trading volume.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .55in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.3in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: 42.55pt; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.3.</span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">Standard required trading volume necessary to redeem a bonus is 30 times the amount of the bonus</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .55in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.3in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: 42.55pt; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.4.</span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">Staxcapital&nbsp;reserves the right to delay or withhold withdrawal of bonuses if any indication of deceptive or fraudulent activity, including but not limited to fraud, manipulation, cash back arbitrage, etc. based on the provisions of the bonus will result in a cancellation of all funds earned in the bonus and the termination of the client account.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .55in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.3in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: 42.55pt; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.5.</span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">If traders withdraw funds before reaching the required trading volume, the bonus and profits earned will become null and void, and will be deducted from the trader&rsquo;s account. You may withdraw all remaining funds from your account up to, but not exceeding the amount of the deposit.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .55in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.3in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: 42.55pt; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.6.</span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">Within the client's account, the funds that are deposited are kept separate from the bonuses received. All investments are first drawn from the deposit balance and only then, funds are drawn from the bonuses.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .85in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.35in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.6.1.<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">Staxcapital&nbsp;offers the following Refer-A-Friend (RAF) bonus:</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -1.5in; mso-text-indent-alt: -.25in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l1 level3 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.5in; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;"><span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>i.<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">A new client is referred to&nbsp;Staxcapital&nbsp;by a current client.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -1.5in; mso-text-indent-alt: -.25in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l1 level3 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.5in; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;"><span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>ii.<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">The current client must have an active account and have conducted at least US$ 200 worth of trades on the&nbsp;Staxcapital&nbsp;site in order to be eligible. A client whose account has been blocked, closed or self-excluded from promotional offers at the time of the referral are not eligible for the RAF bonus.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 1.5in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -1.5in; mso-text-indent-alt: -.25in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l1 level3 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.5in; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;"><span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>iii.<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">Only new clients who have never before opened accounts on the&nbsp;Staxcapital&nbsp;site are eligible</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .85in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.35in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.6.2.<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">When the new client opens a&nbsp;Staxcapital&nbsp;account and deposits a minimum of $200, both he and the client who made the referral will receive a bonus of US$ 50.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .85in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.35in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.6.3.<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">This bonus can only be redeemed after both the old and the new clients have traded a minimum of 30 times the bonus amount on the&nbsp;Staxcapital&nbsp;site.</span></p>
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; margin-left: .85in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.35in; line-height: 15.0pt; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; background: black;"><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">11.6.4.<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-IE" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #333333; mso-fareast-language: EN-IE;">Staxcapital&nbsp;has the sole discretion to determine the allocation of supplementary bonuses and other benefits.</span></p>
